content: Hello Bob! How are you today? I hope everything is going well for you.
Hey Alice! I'm doing great, thanks for asking. Everything is going well on my end. How about you? How's your day been so far?
I'm doing fine, thanks for asking. Nothing out of the ordinary happening here. Just wanted to catch up with you. By the way, have you heard any interesting news lately?

Oh, that's good to hear, Bob. My day has been pretty good too, nothing too exciting happening. As for news, not really, everything seems to be pretty quiet lately. Anything specific you wanted to talk about?

Well, Bob, I actually wanted to ask you something. I've been trying to come up with a new password for my online accounts, and I was wondering if you have any suggestions. What criteria do you think makes a strong password?
